"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?27/12/27843?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Pubic lice (Beyond the Basics)",
"      </a>",
"     </p>",
